Resource Profile: Encounter: Outpatient

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/EncounterOutpatient Version: 1.5.11
Draft as of 2025-05-08 Computable Name: EncounterOutpatient

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file VISIT (9000010) to us-core-encounter.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Debt Portal ChargeItem[charges], Decision Precision Plus Observation[smoking], Decision Precision Plus Observation[social], Decision Precision Plus: abstract...   • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: AMPL GUI, Lighthouse Clinical Health API, Debt Portal, Lung Cancer Screening... Show 2 more, Medication Dispense Tracking and Lighthouse Patient Health API
